notesplaylists: Tibdarin n tɣuri ur ttwasefrakent ara akken iwata. Kra n yismal (am Youku akked Comedy Central) seqdacen tividyutin s ddews n yiḥricen, ttbanent amzun n tibdarin n tɣuri, ihi ur ttwasefrakent ara akken iwata.
notesuncheck: Ma yella amidya ur iseddi ara tafuɣalt n tvidyut neɣ ameslaw, kkes aṛcam n texxamin ilaqen, neɣ, aselket yezmer ur iteddu ara, ɣas akken amasal d ilelli.

extensionmsg: Asiɣzef n ufaylu n ddaw-a yettwaseqdec kan ma yella tavidyut tella deg umasal mačči d ilelli, ayen yesran asettengel. Tividyutin s umasal ilelli ad ḥerzen asiɣzef-nsent.
confirmmsg: Sentem tawuri neɣ sit ɣef 'Uɣal' akken ad tesnifleḍ iɣewwaṛen. Ma tsiteḍ ɣef 'Sentem', tawuri ad tettwazen sakin ad tettwaselkem. Imi llan iɛekkiṛen itiknikanen, tawuri ur tezmir ara ad tettwasefsex s wudm afessas ticki tettwazen.
